---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="FAQ â€” TekMoral" 
  description="Frequently asked questions about TekMoral's services, pricing, and process."
  ogImage="https://www.tekmoral.com/og-faq.png"
>
  <HeroSection
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    description="Find answers to common questions about our services, pricing, and how we work."
    badge="FAQ"
  />

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What services does TekMoral offer?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          We offer four main services: Business Websites & Branding, Custom Web Applications, Tech Consulting & Training, and AI & Machine Learning solutions. Each service is tailored to help businesses and schools modernize their operations and scale efficiently.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How long does a typical project take?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          Project timelines vary based on complexity and scope. A simple website might take 4-8 weeks, while custom applications can take 3-6 months. We'll provide a detailed timeline during your consultation after understanding your specific requirements.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What's your pricing model?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          We offer flexible pricing based on project scope and complexity. Options include fixed-price projects, time-and-materials, and retainer agreements. We'll discuss what works best for your budget during the consultation.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Do you work with startups and small businesses?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          Absolutely! We specialize in working with SMEs, startups, and schools. We understand budget constraints and can create scalable solutions that grow with your business. Many of our clients started as small projects and expanded over time.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>What happens after the project is completed?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          We provide ongoing support and maintenance. This includes bug fixes, updates, and technical support. We can also discuss retainer agreements for continuous improvements and feature additions based on your needs.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>Can you help with digital transformation?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          Yes! Our Tech Consulting & Training service is specifically designed to guide organizations through digital transformation. We assess your current systems, identify opportunities, and create a roadmap for modernization.
        </p>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <details class="group border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-sky-300 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
          <span>How do I get started?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mt-4">
          Simply <a href="/get-started" class="text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 underline">schedule a free consultation</a> with us. We'll discuss your project, answer questions, and create a plan tailored to your needs. No obligation, just a conversation about how we can help.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="bg-sky-50 border border-sky-200 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">Didn't find your answer?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mb-6">
        We're here to help! Reach out to us directly and we'll be happy to answer any questions.
      </p>
      <a href="/get-started" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-400 text-slate-900 font-semibold">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
